/////////////Step1/////////

Win
> Run cmd as admin
> npm install -g create-react-app

Mac/linux
> Open terminal
> sudo npm install -g create-react-app

//////////////Step 2 ///////////////
> Navigate to the folder
> create-react-app firstapp
> cd firstapp
> npm start
> http://localhost:3000/

Functional Component       Class Component
Light in weight              Heavy as compare Functional


